OL,5, Queen's University Belfast (QUB) has   
OL,6, declared a "critical incident" due to  
OL,7, the cost-of-living crisis.             
OL,9,FThe university is due to approve       
OL,10,Fseveral measures to help staff and     
OL,11,Fstudents deal with soaring costs.      
OL,13,FIts vice-chancellor Prof Ian Greer said
OL,14,Fhe wanted to ensure an "appropriate    
OL,15,Finstitutional response".               
OL,17,FQueen's has been allocated #2.7m to be 
OL,18,Fdistributed as hardship funds this     
OL,19,Facademic year as part of a wider       
OL,20,Fsupport package.                       
